{"tid":1839550,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【經濟客飯】處理疫症與政治考慮 - 曾國平","createTime":"2020-01-24T13:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T13:11:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"12d20785a1d91d7c91b4c963087123c1a7d82dc7","tid":1839550,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:02:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200124/BY4ES24UKAJH3VGM5RSYNQVFVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200124%2FBY4ES24UKAJH3VGM5RSYNQVFVE%2F&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77ebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=9426590b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200124%2FBY4ES24UKAJH3VGM5RSYNQVFVE%2F&h=8842dc81\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200124/BY4ES24UKAJH3VGM5RSYNQVFVE/</a><br />\n<br />\n【經濟客飯】處理疫症與政治考慮 - 曾國平<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200124/large/1579797512_81c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200124%2Flarge%2F1579797512_81c4.jpg&h=0c351620&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港的政治制度和內地越走越近，當然包括處理疫症消息通報等政策。資料圖片<br />\n(社內相)<br />\n<br />\n回想幾個月前，大家還在討論香港經濟會否差過沙士，想不到這個「假設性問題」，現時忽然好有現實意義。再回帶六年幾以前，我在友報這樣寫：「歷史有甚麼教訓？沙士的經濟影響來得快、去得快，靠的是香港政府把資訊公開，既詳細教育市民如何防範沙士，亦一五一十的把感染、死亡數字展示人前，不隱瞞疫情。公開資訊有助抑制沙士擴散，資訊亦能使香港市民及外國人對政府有信心。」今天重讀，感覺複雜，尤其是跟穆迪調低香港信貸評級的決定一起看，越看越耐人尋味。<br />\n<br />\n對的，香港有處理沙士經驗，今天科技亦比十幾年前進步，會給疫症的破壞力打折扣。可是，今天香港跟當年大不同，and not in a good way。講實際情況，除了香港跟內地交通流量已大大增加，亦有太多例子告訴我們，政府官員越來越注重政治正確，從嚴重應變級別已是「先行前一步」，到因怕大批人滯留而不要求高鐵乘客填表，難免令人聯想到有不敢比中央走得更前的政治考慮，只怕背上製造恐慌的罪名。<br />\n<br />\n講信心預期，正如穆迪等評級機構所講，外界認為香港的政治制度和內地越走越近，當然包括處理疫症消息通報等政策，對香港政府的信心不及當年。希望我只是杞人憂天，香港能夠避過一劫，差唔過沙士。<br />\n<br />\n曾國平<br />\n美國維珍尼亞理工大學經濟系副教授<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/economics3.0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Feconomics3.0%2F&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77ebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=c0080b7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/economics3.0/</a><br />\n本欄逢周五刊出"},{"pid":"e8ac2ca773259a415fba894ef1b9f665adfac6a8","tid":1839550,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:03:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"c06a34952ae6f7c2513c3c1e69e4312d7a3d2531","tid":1839550,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:11:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"}]}